{"tid":1197284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"去遊行時聽到大會咁講","createTime":"2019-06-10T02:51:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T03:19:10.000Z","uid":183971,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"997ac7501061cdd47f29b45feed5073798fa7a46","tid":1197284,"uid":183971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T02:51:19.000Z","msg":"其實大台都唔想播歌<br />\n但我地得幾個人講野會攰<br />\n所以我地先利用播歌的時間休息下<br />\n<br />\n你地信唔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"232b59ae1a70ab6afdd73aa30359c3c5fbf6da96","tid":1197284,"uid":44171,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T02:52:18.000Z","msg":"目的係磨損民眾體力同意志<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da6de21c7d397a5556a3fb933816ad5fa4d64a40","tid":1197284,"uid":183971,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"232b59ae1a70ab6afdd73aa30359c3c5fbf6da96","tid":1197284,"uid":44171,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T02:52:18.000Z","msg":"目的係磨損民眾體力同意志<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T02:53:31.000Z","msg":"咁就變成嘉年華會"},{"pid":"78e7e8659d7e159ea05cbe28f28500b60b0e9139","tid":1197284,"uid":80814,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T03:00:56.000Z","msg":"其實佢地唔好講咁多廢話，嗰啲咩就算輸，香港人已經打咗場美麗嘅仗，同叫人打卡自拍，唔好講，喉嚨自然唔會咁攰。<br />\n<br />\n同埋遊行最重要係反送中，但林鄭下台嘅口號竟然嗌得仲多。最後仲有連嗌林鄭林鄭林鄭嚟埋尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大台最重要係傳遞到現場信息，例如邊度封咗，邊度人多塞，同邊度未開行車線，而唔係唱歌搞氣氛。"},{"pid":"8d8c735aabf406155d314187ada28ab045d85c0e","tid":1197284,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T03:04:35.000Z","msg":"仲有叫籌款嗰班唔好咁過份，屌那星，民間電台叫人有嗌口號就要畀錢佢呀"},{"pid":"6fee9d21dfb4ed12da8447275abb01c3a5527c15","tid":1197284,"uid":183971,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8d8c735aabf406155d314187ada28ab045d85c0e","tid":1197284,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T03:04:35.000Z","msg":"仲有叫籌款嗰班唔好咁過份，屌那星，民間電台叫人有嗌口號就要畀錢佢呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T03:06:08.000Z","msg":"我明白免費裝水呢樣係好好<br />\n有人自發出來refill<br />\n<br />\n其實我都想捐比佢地<br />\n不過唔知點捐<br />\n<br />\n唔想捐比政棍"},{"pid":"a1043c572ac0868f847e11760991316524054782","tid":1197284,"uid":183971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T03:07:03.000Z","msg":"人民力量仲要開咪大大聲講呀邊個都來遊行<br />\n<br />\n驚死冇人知佢係度<br />\n<br />\n正一豬隊友"},{"pid":"0c6ada21593551616dcf38d052292d0f14f8a4fe","tid":1197284,"uid":71509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T03:08:38.000Z","msg":"佢都on9<br />\n<br />\n有班人係鵝頸橋到打鼓<br />\n<br />\n士氣幾撚好<br />\n<br />\n我寧願你播鼓聲"},{"pid":"83112b5cdeeb7ae641aa5ccb77635c5fdc2916bd","tid":1197284,"uid":183971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T03:09:53.000Z","msg":"大家揮揮手<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a44be8bb50378bb0ad41686ff269fec4b8eefef7","tid":1197284,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1043c572ac0868f847e11760991316524054782","tid":1197284,"uid":183971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T03:07:03.000Z","msg":"人民力量仲要開咪大大聲講呀邊個都來遊行<br />\n<br />\n驚死冇人知佢係度<br />\n<br />\n正一豬隊友"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T03:12:18.000Z","msg":"快必真係好撚趕客，永遠鳩吓鳩吓咁"},{"pid":"d8c39e8a91d254312781fa4920911c5c51f634bf","tid":1197284,"uid":183971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a44be8bb50378bb0ad41686ff269fec4b8eefef7","tid":1197284,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1043c572ac0868f847e11760991316524054782","tid":1197284,"uid":183971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T03:07:03.000Z","msg":"人民力量仲要開咪大大聲講呀邊個都來遊行<br />\n<br />\n驚死冇人知佢係度<br />\n<br />\n正一豬隊友"},"citedBy":